39:39.280 --> 39:41.840
Your contract is in it too.

39:42.120 --> 39:44.720
This is a token of my gratitude.

39:45.480 --> 39:47.600
Lady, if I did something wrong...

39:47.680 --> 39:48.880
Please punish me.

39:48.960 --> 39:50.200
I have no objection.

39:50.280 --> 39:52.560
Don't kick me out, girl.

39:52.640 --> 39:53.920
- wake up.
- ma'am

39:54.000 --> 39:55.600
I'm not kicking you out.

39:57.080 --> 40:00.440
This is a wedding gift given to Nanfeng when he marries her.

40:02.000 --> 40:03.840
Girl, I don't want to leave you.

40:04.360 --> 40:05.960
Saya dan Nanfeng cuma...

40:06.960 --> 40:10.120
I may have to leave Hwangcheong soon.

40:11.280 --> 40:13.280
Luckily, I get it now.

40:13.360 --> 40:15.200
If not,
I'll take you...

40:15.280 --> 40:16.960
And it destroys your happiness.

40:17.360 --> 40:18.400
Wherever you go...

40:18.480 --> 40:20.000
I will go with you.

40:21.600 --> 40:22.640
don't worry.

40:22.720 --> 40:24.440
Jika Nanfeng buli wake nanti...

40:24.520 --> 40:25.680
Even though it's not in Hwangcheong...

40:25.760 --> 40:27.320
I will come back to protect you
.

40:28.080 --> 40:30.560
No, I'll go with you.

40:32.120 --> 40:34.040
Why do you want to come with me?

40:34.120 --> 40:36.480
This marriage
involves your whole life.

40:36.560 --> 40:38.000
Nan Feng is a good person...

40:38.080 --> 40:39.760
And you love each other.

40:39.840 --> 40:41.000
You don't have to worry about me.

40:42.160 --> 40:44.640
After all, I
can't afford to hire you forever.

40:44.720 --> 40:45.880
So don't think about relying on me.

40:50.640 --> 40:53.080
When
did you start having feelings for Nanfeng?

40:53.160 --> 40:54.560
Why didn't you tell me?

40:54.840 --> 40:57.320
Are you afraid that I will bother you?

40:57.720 --> 41:00.080
I just found out how he was feeling a few days ago.

41:00.160 --> 41:02.720
All this time I
thought he liked you.

41:03.800 --> 41:05.240
I didn't tell you...

41:05.320 --> 41:09.000
Because I think it's impossible between us.

41:09.080 --> 41:10.560
impossible?

41:10.840 --> 41:12.560
I am now open minded...

41:12.640 --> 41:13.720
And those are two different things.

41:13.800 --> 41:15.160
Conflict between Jong Ye-ran and me...

41:15.240 --> 41:17.480
There is no need to involve anyone else.

41:19.360 --> 41:21.640
Miss said she wanted to leave Huangcheng
.

41:21.720 --> 41:22.880
Where do you want to go?

41:24.040 --> 41:25.080
Who knows?

41:25.360 --> 41:28.280
Anyway,
I don't want to get stuck here.

41:28.360 --> 41:29.760
The world is wide.

41:29.840 --> 41:31.880
I need to go out and
expand my experience.

41:31.960 --> 41:32.960
right?

41:33.120 --> 41:34.200
We
postpone until the time comes.

41:38.120 --> 41:41.120
When you find someone you like
...

41:41.200 --> 41:42.640
Please tell me right away.

41:42.720 --> 41:43.760
It doesn't matter who that person is.

41:43.840 --> 41:44.880
If he is the man you want to marry...

41:44.960 --> 41:46.600
I
will marry you in style.

41:51.360 --> 41:53.440
Selagi cik di Huangcheng...

41:53.520 --> 41:54.960
I'll be with you.

41:55.680 --> 41:57.520
Should we go quickly?

41:58.680 --> 42:00.760
- to let go!
- Decent.

42:01.040 --> 42:02.840
Go get some wedding gifts...

42:03.160 --> 42:05.600
Help prepare food.

42:05.680 --> 42:07.200
I want to go to Bell Park.

42:07.560 --> 42:08.640
Want to go to Taman Zhong?

42:09.800 --> 42:12.080
great.
For your happiness...

42:12.160 --> 42:13.520
I can't wait any longer.

42:13.600 --> 42:16.000
We need to solve this problem quickly
.

42:25.280 --> 42:28.080
<i>Lakaman Bonus</i>

42:29.240 --> 42:31.800
Is Hwang your real name?

42:32.120 --> 42:35.680
No, Tuan Muda Hua
gave me that name.

42:36.480 --> 42:38.080
So what is your real name?

42:38.520 --> 42:39.520
Huang Aotian.

42:40.480 --> 42:43.680
Why did you change your name to Hwang?

42:43.760 --> 42:45.000
Young Master Hua said.

42:45.080 --> 42:48.200
I think my name is so noble.

42:48.280 --> 42:50.760
As
if I were the owner and not him.

42:50.840 --> 42:52.240
So I changed my name...

42:52.320 --> 42:53.760
With a name that is easy to remember.

43:00.600 --> 43:02.280
That
seems like something he would do.

